    <!-- ABOUT -->
    <section id="about">
      <h2 class="sec-title" data-en="About" data-zh="关于">About</h2>
      <p class="lang-en about-text">
        I am a PhD candidate (combined Master–PhD) at the School of Applied Economics,
        <strong>Renmin University of China (RUC)</strong>.
        My research lies at the intersection of <strong>energy industry policy</strong> and
        <strong>low-carbon development</strong>, focusing on electricity market design,
        new energy industrial policy, and China's energy transition.
        I have published in <em>Energy Policy</em>, <em>Energy Economics</em>, and
        <em>Economics and Human Biology</em>.
      </p>
      <p class="lang-zh about-text" style="display:none">
        本人就读于<strong>中国人民大学应用经济学院</strong>，能源经济学专业（硕博连读，保研直博）。
        研究聚焦于<strong>能源产业政策</strong>与<strong>低碳发展</strong>，
        重点方向包括电力市场设计、新能源产业政策及中国能源转型。
        已在 <em>Energy Policy</em>、<em>Energy Economics</em>、<em>Economics and Human Biology</em> 等期刊发表成果。
      </p>

